  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Established diagnosis of atransferrinemia, defined as serum levels of transferrin
             below 40 mg/dl

          -  Informed consent

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Known with allergic reactions against human plasma or plasma products

          -  Having detectable anti-immunoglobulin A antibodies
      </textblock>
